ing special . So I ca n't say anything negative about them.<br /><br />The story and movie is far from original . It rip - offs from a lot of classic and semi - classic , mostly modern , science - fiction movies . It perhaps is also the reason why the movie made a very redundant impression on me.<br /><br />A failed and uninteresting movie experiment.<br /><br />3/10
