0 A bondage , humiliation , S&M show , and not much else . The plot is flat , really just a banal setup for the stylishly depraved set - pieces . The host of the aforementioned show , a silly little man who spouts drivel while prancing around the stage in dresses , was almost as painfully distracting as the attempts at artful editing . The dream - like ending felt tacked on . To the film 's credit though , Aya Sugimoto was fairly convincing as the tortured lead . Flower and Snake has been compared with Eyes Wide Shut but aside from some minor surface similarities , Kubrick 's is easily the more layered , artistic , and atmospheric picture .
